            bindings = <
        &kp Q  &kp W           &kp F             &kp P        &kp B      &kp J      &kp L        &kp U                &kp Y             &mt DOUBLE_QUOTES SQT
        &kp A  &mt LEFT_ALT R  &mt LEFT_SHIFT S  &mt LCTRL T  &kp G      &kp M      &mt RCTRL N  &mt RIGHT_SHIFT E    &mt RALT I        &kp O
&trans  &kp Z  &kp X           &kp C             &kp D        &kp V      &kp K      &kp H        &mt SEMICOLON COMMA  &mt COLON PERIOD  &mt BACKSLASH SLASH    &mt QUESTION EXCLAMATION
                               &trans            &kp SPACE    &kp TAB    &kp ENTER  &kp BSPC     &kp DELETE
