          &trans    &mt MINUS EQUAL    &kp N7             &kp N8            &kp N9     &kp LS(EXCL)   &kp LS(AT)               &kp LS(POUND)                 &kp LS(DLLR)                        &kp LS(PRCNT)
          &kp UP    &mt LEFT_ALT PLUS  &mt LEFT_SHIFT N4  &mt LCTRL N5      &kp N6     &kp LS(CARET)  &mt LS(RCTRL) AMPERSAND  &mt LS(RIGHT_SHIFT) ASTERISK  &mt LS(RIGHT_ALT) LEFT_PARENTHESIS  &kp LS(RPAR)
